---
title: Crispy Cajun Catfish with Collard Greens and Grilled Corn
description: Crusted catfish, collard greens, and sweet, golden corn—we must be going down South for dinner tonight! Three hallmark ingredients are put together in this dish that’s full of Cajun-style character. The fish is rubbed with our blend of garlic, paprika, and herbs, then coated in a layer of panko that provides a satisfying crunch next to the tender veggies.
